FIX FCT (FixFCT) – Website & Mobile App

Together we can Fix the FCT.








Overview

FIX FCT is a civic technology initiative designed to empower residents of Nigeria's Federal Capital Territory (FCT) to actively participate in building better communities through technology, transparency, and collaboration.

The platform consists of a responsive website and mobile application that enable citizens to:

Report community issues
Suggest practical solutions
Track government and community projects
Volunteer for development initiatives
Participate in surveys and polls
Access verified information
Engage with elected representatives
Promote accountability and transparent governance

Our mission is simple:

Together we can Fix the FCT.

Vision

To build the most trusted digital civic engagement platform for the Federal Capital Territory, connecting citizens, communities, and leadership through technology.

Mission

To provide innovative digital tools that empower every resident to contribute to the development of the Federal Capital Territory.

Core Objectives
Improve citizen participation
Increase government accountability
Promote transparency
Encourage community development
Support data-driven decision making
Build stronger communities
